00:10:08.549 --> 00:10:11.309
in the truth.

00:10:11.309 --> 00:10:16.070
The words safeguard your heart caught my eye.

00:10:16.070 --> 00:10:24.669
I decided to try and keep my heart and my children's hearts towards Jehovah.

00:10:24.669 --> 00:10:30.549
When I went out in the ministry with my children, I would point out various aspects of God's

00:10:30.549 --> 00:10:33.309
creation around us.

00:10:33.309 --> 00:10:38.830
And before my husband would come home from work, I made it a habit to teach them God's

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:40.629
word.

00:10:40.629 --> 00:10:47.110
I made a conscious effort to see myself in paradise with my husband.

00:10:47.110 --> 00:10:52.230
This strengthened my resolve to never leave the truth.

00:10:52.230 --> 00:10:57.269
I wrote caring notes to my husband when I went to the meetings.

00:10:57.269 --> 00:11:02.789
I was convinced that he would come back one day.

00:11:02.789 --> 00:11:05.549
And he did come back.

00:11:05.549 --> 00:11:12.389
I did not leave Jehovah and so Jehovah never abandoned me.

00:11:12.389 --> 00:11:15.950
My husband never embraced the truth.

00:11:15.950 --> 00:11:26.110
However, right now, all five of my children are in the truth and I feel really blessed.

00:11:26.110 --> 00:11:33.230
Being able to serve Jehovah as a family, along with my husband, the joy and appreciation

00:11:33.230 --> 00:11:38.820
just keep dwelling up.

00:11:38.820 --> 00:11:42.620
What did we learn from the video?

00:11:42.620 --> 00:11:48.740
We learned that believing mates who display fine Christian qualities can have a positive

00:11:48.740 --> 00:11:53.179
influence on mates who are not yet serving Jehovah.

00:11:53.179 --> 00:11:59.220
So what will help you to keep on fighting for the faith?

00:11:59.220 --> 00:12:04.059
Wisdom and strength that only Jehovah can provide.

00:12:04.059 --> 00:12:12.379
Remember, his power is unlimited and he finds pleasure in showing favor to those who trust

00:12:12.379 --> 00:12:14.899
in him.

00:12:14.899 --> 00:12:20.740
So you know that he loves you and that he listens to sincere prayers from those who want

00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:24.669
to do things his way.

00:12:24.669 --> 00:12:31.710
The combination of God's love, prayer and his spirit can give you the strength and the

00:12:31.710 --> 00:12:38.789
wisdom you need to maintain a balanced routine of spiritual activities while making sure to

00:12:38.789 --> 00:12:44.149
care for your family responsibilities.

00:12:44.149 --> 00:12:50.950
In the video, the believing mates took advantage of all the spiritual food that was available

00:12:50.950 --> 00:12:53.990
to build themselves up.

00:12:53.990 --> 00:13:00.590
