00:13:00.590 --> 00:13:07.190
You know as well as I do that at times we may not be as tactful as we should be.

00:13:07.190 --> 00:13:14.549
Being patient and tactful is not always easy, especially when you're tired and feel

00:13:14.549 --> 00:13:19.470
disappointed by your mates' words or actions.

00:13:19.470 --> 00:13:27.590
And yet, regardless of your situation, Jehovah can supply you with the power to keep setting

00:13:27.590 --> 00:13:37.129
a fine example as you keep on praying that your mate will eventually respond to the truth.

